Each use of the Software, defined as any execution, invocation, deployment, automated call, embedded operation, or protocol-level utilization, requires payment of a non-refundable usage fee.

Fee Terms

Amount: 0.01 (unit defined by implementation)

Frequency: Per use

Recipient: Blockchain address specified within the Software or its configuration

Settlement Medium: Blockchain network specified within the Software

Payment must occur prior to or concurrently with use.

